*                                      EXERC2.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC2.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC2.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
     2     PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC2.
     3     AUTHOR.        YHAGO.
     4     DATE-WRITTEN.  14/06/25.
     5     DATE-COMPILED.
     6     SECURITY.      SOMENTE O AUTOR PODE MODIFICALO.
     7 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
     8 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
     9     SPECIAL-NAMES.  DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    10 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    11 FILE-CONTROL.
    12     SELECT CADANT ASSIGN TO DISK
    13     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    14     SELECT ARQMOV ASSIGN TO DISK
    15     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    16     SELECT  CADATU ASSIGN TO DISK
    17     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    18     SELECT RELOCORR ASSIGN TO DISK
    19     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    20 DATA DIVISION.
    21 FILE SECTION.
    22
    23 FD CADANT
    24     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    25     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADANT.DAT".
    26 01 REG-ANT.
    27     02 CC-ANT        PIC 9(03).
    28     02 TIPO-ANT      PIC X(01).
    29     02 ENDER-ANT     PIC X(50).
    30 FD ARQMOV
    31     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    32     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "ARQMOV.DAT".
    33 01 REG-MOV.
    34     02 CC-MOV        PIC 9(03).
    35     02 TIPO-MOV      PIC X(01).
    36     02 ENDER-MOV     PIC X(50).
    37 FD CADATU
    38     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    39     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADATU.DAT".
    40 01 REG-ATU.
    41     02 CC-ATU       PIC 9(03).
    42     02 TIPO-ATU     PIC X(01).
    43     02 ENDER-ATU    PIC X(50).
    44 FD RELOCORR
    45     LABEL RECORD  OMITTED.
    46 01 REG-ATR      PIC X(80).
    47 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    48     77 CH-CADANT PIC  X(04) VALUE SPACES.
    49     77 CH-ARQMOV PIC  X(04) VALUE SPACES.
    50     77 CH-TYPE   PIC  X(02) VALUE SPACES.
    51     77 CT-LIN           PIC 9(02) VALUE 40.
    52     77 CT-PAG           PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROS.
    53 01 WHITE-CAB.
    54     02 FILLER     PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
    55 01 CAB-01.
    56     02 FILLER     PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
    57     02 FILLER     PIC X(22) VALUE "Relaçăo de atualizaçăo".
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 16-Jun-25 16:07 Page   2
*                                      EXERC2.CBL
    58     02 FILLER     PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.
    59     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE "PAG. ".
    60     02 VAR-PAG    PIC ZZ9.
    61 01 CAB-02.
    62     02 FILLER     PIC X(06) VALUE "codigo".
    63     02 FILLER     PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
    64     02 FILLER     PIC X(04) VALUE "tipo".
    65     02 FILLER     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    66     02 FILLER     PIC X(08) VALUE "mensagem".
    67
    68 01 DETALHE.
    69     02 FILLER        PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
    70     02 VAR-COD       PIC ZZ9.
    71     02 FILLER        PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    72     02 VAR-TIPO      PIC X(01) .
    73     02 FILLER        PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
    74     02 VAR-MSG       PIC X(50).
    75
    76 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    77 PGM-04.
    78 PERFORM INICIO.
    79 PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    80     UNTIL CH-CADANT EQUAL CH-ARQMOV AND
    81     CH-ARQMOV EQUAL   HIGH-VALUES.
    82 PERFORM FIM.
    83 STOP RUN.
    84 INICIO.
    85     OPEN INPUT CADANT
    86                ARQMOV
    87          OUTPUT CADATU RELOCORR.
    88     PERFORM LER-CADANT.
    89     PERFORM LER-ARQMOV.
    90
    91 LER-CADANT.
    92     READ CADANT AT END MOVE HIGH-VALUE TO CH-CADANT.
    93     IF  NOT(CH-CADANT EQUAL HIGH-VALUE)
    94         MOVE CC-ANT TO CH-CADANT
    95     END-IF.
    96 LER-ARQMOV.
    97     READ ARQMOV AT END MOVE HIGH-VALUE TO CH-ARQMOV.
    98     IF  NOT(CH-ARQMOV EQUAL HIGH-VALUE)
    99         MOVE CC-MOV TO CH-ARQMOV
   100     END-IF.
   101 PRINCIPAL.
   102     IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "I" OR TIPO-MOV EQUAL "E" OR TIPO-MOV
   103                                                    EQUAL "A"
   104         IF CH-CADANT EQUAL CH-ARQMOV
   105             PERFORM IGUAL
   106             PERFORM GRAVACAO-REL
   107             PERFORM LER-CADANT
   108             PERFORM LER-ARQMOV
   109         ELSE IF CH-CADANT LESS CH-ARQMOV
   110             PERFORM CADANT-MENOR
   111             PERFORM LER-CADANT
   112         ELSE IF CH-ARQMOV LESS CH-CADANT
   113             PERFORM ARQMOV-MENOR
   114             PERFORM GRAVACAO-REL
   115             PERFORM LER-ARQMOV
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 16-Jun-25 16:07 Page   3
*                                      EXERC2.CBL
   116         END-IF
   117     ELSE
   118         PERFORM LER-ARQMOV
   119     END-IF.
   120
   121 IGUAL.
   122     IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "I"
   123         MOVE "EI" TO CH-TYPE
   124         PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA-2
   125     ELSE IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "A"
   126         MOVE "EA" TO CH-TYPE
   127         PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA-1
   128     ELSE IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "E"
   129         MOVE "EE" TO CH-TYPE
   130     END-IF.
   131 ARQMOV-MENOR.
   132     IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "I"
   133         MOVE "MI" TO CH-TYPE
   134         PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA-1
   135     ELSE IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "A"
   136         MOVE "MA" TO CH-TYPE
   137     ELSE IF TIPO-MOV EQUAL "E"
   138         MOVE "ME" TO CH-TYPE
   139     END-IF.
   140 CADANT-MENOR.
   141     PERFORM GRAVACAO-SAIDA-2.
   142 GRAVACAO-SAIDA-1.
   143     MOVE CC-MOV TO CC-ATU
   144     MOVE TIPO-MOV TO TIPO-ATU
   145     MOVE ENDER-MOV TO ENDER-ATU
   146     WRITE REG-ATU.
   147 GRAVACAO-SAIDA-2.
   148     MOVE CC-ANT TO CC-ATU
   149     MOVE TIPO-ANT TO TIPO-ATU
   150     MOVE ENDER-ANT TO ENDER-ATU
   151     WRITE REG-ATU.
   152 GRAVACAO-REL.
   153     IF CT-LIN GREATER THAN 39
   154         PERFORM CABECALHO-01
   155     END-IF.
   156     PERFORM DETALHES.
   157
   158 DETALHES.
   159     MOVE CC-MOV TO VAR-COD
   160     MOVE TIPO-MOV TO VAR-TIPO
   161     IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "EI"
   162         MOVE "INCLUSĂO P/REG. JÁ EXISTENTE" TO VAR-MSG
   163     ELSE IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "EE"
   164         MOVE "REGISTRO EXCLUIDO" TO VAR-MSG
   165     ELSE IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "EA"
   166         MOVE TIPO-ANT TO VAR-TIPO
   167         MOVE "REGISTRO SUBSTITUIDO" TO VAR-MSG
   168         WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   169         MOVE TIPO-MOV TO VAR-TIPO
   170         MOVE "REGISTRO SUBSTITUTO" TO VAR-MSG
   171         ADD 1 TO CT-LIN
   172     ELSE IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "MI"
   173         MOVE "REGISTRO INCLUIDO" TO VAR-MSG
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 16-Jun-25 16:07 Page   4
*                                      EXERC2.CBL
   174     ELSE IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "MA"
   175         MOVE "ALTERAÇĂO P/REG. INEXISTENTE" TO VAR-MSG
   176     ELSE IF CH-TYPE EQUAL "ME"
   177         MOVE "EXCLUSĂO P/REG. INEXISTENTE" TO VAR-MSG
   178     END-IF.
   179     WRITE REG-ATR FROM DETALHE AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE
   180
   181     ADD 1 TO CT-LIN.
   182
   183 CABECALHO-01.
   184     ADD 1         TO CT-PAG.
   185     MOVE CT-PAG   TO VAR-PAG.
   186     MOVE SPACES   TO REG-ATR.
   187     WRITE REG-ATR AFTER ADVANCING PAGE.
   188     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-01 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   189     WRITE REG-ATR FROM WHITE-CAB AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   190     WRITE REG-ATR FROM CAB-02 AFTER ADVANCING 1 LINE.
   191     MOVE 4  TO CT-LIN.
   192
   193 FIM.
   194     CLOSE CADANT CADATU ARQMOV RELOCORR.
